title: Kelly Ripa Part 2 & Camila Mendes

description:
This week’s Unqualified brings you more SDCC interviews. First, some hilarious Kelly Ripa bonus material in which Anna, Kelly and Sim discuss talk show jitters, and female envy, and tips for new parents. Then, Camila Mendes (RIVERDALE) joins Anna and Sim on the SDCC boat! Camila and Anna touch on past SDCC experiences. Then, Camila answers some deal breakers, explains why cats are the way to her heart, and they call Haley who wants the boy she’s seeing to text back more promptly.
